The '''Acme Rocket''' is [[ACME Inc|ACME]]'s mid-catalogue product, launched in 2010 as the company's first move beyond the [[Acme Anvil|Anvil]] line. Its release prompted the opening of the [[ACME Vienna Office|Vienna office]] to support central European customers.

The Rocket is a more dynamic counterpart to the Anvil and is maintained by the same [[ACME Engineering|engineering team]] in [[Amsterdam]].
